item.title: Nine Useless Jack O' Lantern Templates
item.description: Most of these were taken from the huge catalog of templates over at Stoneykins.com, the vast majority of which are pretty cool and definitely not useless. #9. Joker Joaquin Phoenix Already looks like you messed it up. Badly. #8. Boo-Tay Why. #7. Frank Sinatra Stein No. #6. Two Youts Nothing says classic Halloween nostalgia like My Cousin Vinny. 5. Kim Jong Un Wouldn’t “Rocket Man” be more appropriate for the 4th of July?
